name: ColorsofNatureScreensaverforEchoShow
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my nature
des:
Colors of Nature Screensaver HD on your Echo Show or Echo Spot device (required a screen). Enjoy the peaceful and colorful nature views in beautiful HD on your Echo Show, Echo Spot or Fire TV. Relax with beautiful birds, flowers, and more!.. Music for relaxation, sleep, meditation, yoga, study. Sit back, relax and enjoy :)

+ Ask "Alexa, open my nature" to open skill. Enjoy!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
